name: Cubedise 2
description:
WARNING:the game is currently in obt (open beta testing) if you find a bug or flaw delivered to sdfstudiosdev@gmail.com, also describing where and how you found this bug.we will be grateful to you

cubedise 2 is an unofficial continuation of the game from sdf studios, which was removed from the play market by the rexet studio. we want to revive the game and here it is.This game is in the puzzle genre fron the first person. you got into the strange world of cubes and sent you there to explore it.your task is to interact with colorful cubes to pass to the next level.This game has regular updates. new blocks, new levels, russian and english laungage and chapters.
